description: The video shows an animation of a blond woman dressed in a dark blue outfit that has cutouts on the upper chest. The woman has dark blue or purple fingernails, red lips, fair skin, and blond, curly hair. Initially, she has small, purple horns and is holding a large flame in her open hand. Her eyes are purple. She smirks. Then, her eyes change to blue and she removes the horns. She licks her finger and looks to the side.
